  "title": "Housekeeper",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Clean and maintain guest room, carpet, flooring, wallpapers, furniture and bathrooms daily. Clean and make up rooms and bathrooms according to Hotel's standards and procedures</li>\n  <li>Conduct duties in courteous, safe and efficient manner, in accordance with hotel and governement's policies and procedures, ensuring that the highest level of service and communication is maintained</li>\n  <li>Equip trolley with adequate supplies and keeps trolley/ pantry neat and tidy at all times</li>\n  <li>Cover laundry duty. Collect and deliver guest laundry, counting soil linen and distribute clean linen</li>\n  <li>Report suspicious persons or actions, DND rooms according to procedures. Report room discrepancy accurately and follow standard procedure</li>\n  <li>Cleaning of public areas within hotel premises. Carry out special project and tasks such as shampooing of carpets and taking stock</li>\n</ul>",
